			<h1>About Curator.io</h1>
			<p>Everyone loves to collect. Some people treasure their collection of antique stamps while others collect life size statues of princess Leia. Whatever you collect, nothing is more fun then showing off your collection to friends, family and fellow enthusiasts. We want to bring that feeling to the internet, that's why we created Curator.io!</p>
			<p>Curator.io is the first cloud based collection app that allows you to effortlessly Upload, Personalize and Share your collections. We combine powerful tools like custom data fields and deep Facebook Opengraph integration with an easy to use user interface.</p>
			<PCollectors come in all shapes and sizes and we believe everyone is a collector of some sort. Curator.io is build to accommodate even the most die hard of data geeks while still being totally accessible to the novice collector.</p>
